aott/analysis/hotpath_analysis/hotpath_detector.runa
Hot Path Detection Module for AOTT Tier Promotion

This module provides hot path detection for the Runa AOTT system including:
- Execution frequency analysis
- Hot path identification algorithms
- Call chain hotness propagation
- Loop nest hotness analysis
- Function-level hotness ranking
- Dynamic hotness threshold adjustment
- Hot path stability tracking
- Multi-tier hotness classification
- Hot path merging and splitting
- Profile-guided hot path detection
- Temporal hotness patterns
- Hotness decay modeling
- Hot path prediction
- Cross-compilation unit hotness
- Hot path visualization and reporting
:End Note

